Haven't tried recipe yet, going to, but to answer previous reviewers question about toasting bran; put the bran in a dry, large heavyweight skillet over medium-low heat. Cook, stirring with a whisk, until the bran is well toasted and dark, but not scorched, about 10 minutes.

